  "prompt": "What are funniest incidents you had with your friends?",
  "response": "I don't have personal experiences or friends, but I can share some common funny incidents that people often experience with their friends:\n\n1. **Mismatched Outfits**: Going out for a casual hangout and realizing that you and your friend wore matching outfits, or even better, the same quirky graphic tee, which turns into a fun photo-op.\n\n2. **Texting Fails**: Sending a text meant for one friend to the wrong friend, leading to humorous misunderstandings, especially if it\u2019s about them!\n\n3. **Cooking Disasters**: Attempting to cook a meal together, only to realize halfway through that one of the main ingredients is missing. This often leads to creative (and usually hilarious) substitutions.\n\n4. **The Prank Wars**: Engaging in light-hearted pranks, like hiding each other\u2019s belongings or setting up silly surprises, which can escalate into a creative battle of wits.\n\n5. **Awkward Encounters**: Meeting someone they used to date at an unexpected place and awkwardly trying to navigate that while trying to keep it casual, often leading to inside jokes later.\n\n6. **Misheard Lyrics**: Singing along to a song and realizing that you\u2019ve been singing the wrong lyrics for years, only to have your friends join in and make it a group laughter moment.\n\n7. **Epic Fail Photos**: Taking a group photo, only for one person to be caught mid-blink or making a silly face, which turns into the group\u2019s favorite meme.\n\nThese types of incidents often create memorable moments and inside jokes that friendships thrive on!",
